1. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the victorian house##8
3. the victorian house is on the right of the cottage house##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
