There are 2 different nationalities: mexican, pakistani
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, volleyball
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, vegafina
1. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the havana-smoker is not the person watching drama movies##6
4. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the havana-smoker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Movie-Genre   | drama      | time-travel |
| Nationality   | mexican    | pakistani   |
| Sport         | volleyball | sailing     |
| Cigar     | vegafina | havana  |

